Dear naive miners - **do basic math**
About 1/3 of miners get randomly 0 weights on bittensor during 1/4 of the day, that's 20/4 = ~5 bittensor epochs, therefore up to 3*5=15 registrations will be rotated a day _regardless_ of performance.
